---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: 标签
lang: zh
description: 按标签浏览博客文章。
permalink: /zh/blog/tags/
---

<section class="blog-list">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-title">
      <h1>标签</h1>
      <p>按标签浏览博客文章。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tag-cloud">
      {% for tag in collections.zhTagList %}
      <a href="/zh/blog/tags/{{ tag | slugify }}/" class="tag-link">
        {{ tag }}
        <span class="tag-count">({{ collections.zhPostsByTag[tag].length }})</span>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    {% if collections.zhTagList.length == 0 %}
    <div class="text-center" style="padding: var(--space-16) 0;">
      <p>暂无标签，请稍后再来！</p>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>
